com.iasmar.rome.ui.views.base

Class BasePresenter<V extends IBaseView>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iasmar.rome.ui.views.base.BasePresenter<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The view.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBasePresenter<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EngineersPresenter, MainPresenter, SchedulesPresenter

    public class BasePresenter<V extends IBaseView>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBasePresenter<V>
    Created by Asmar on 01/7/2018.

    Base class that implements the Presenter interface and provides a base implementation for onAttach() and onDetach(). It also handles keeping a reference to the mvpView that can be accessed from the children classes by calling getMvpView(), It also handles errors.

    Since:
    1.0
